Replace cinematic with engineering Process Flow Diagram

The illustrated factory/cubes/smokestacks read as childish. Replaced with
a scroll-constructed PFD that builds itself across four chapters:

* Title block, axis ticks, drawing-frame corner crosshairs, blueprint grid
